title: Kylie Jenner Shows Off Post Travis Scott Breakup HOTNESS With Multiple Bikini Shots
text:
Kylie Jenner decided to take a girls' trip and get away for the weekend, and she is showing baby daddy Travis Scott exactly what he is missing now that the couple has split.

Jenner posted several bikini shots from her vacation, including two in a pink bikini that is making the whole internet blush.

The makeup mogul simply captioned the photo, "girls trip."

Kylie posted another photo including her friend, Yris Palmer, where the duo is posing next to a beautiful infinity pool.

The Kardashian sisters got in on the action commenting on Kylie's post, with Kim saying, "WOW" and Khloe posting "Dammmmnnnnnn."

Girls Trip!

Kylie has been posting a few photos on Instagram that could be interpreted as messages to her ex Travis Scott. A few days ago, she posted several photos of herself laying topless in bed.

Bedtime....

Travis Scott and Kylie Jenner have broken up for a few weeks now, but we are told the stars have agreed to split 50/50 custody and co-parent their daughter as they work things out.
